  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要梳理一下基础设施的核心组件关系。首先，Redis缓存层作为高频访问的组件，应该直接和Etcd集群交互，用于配置同步。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Audit",
        "Define"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，Audit指向Define。那IngressController这块呢？我们有两个实例对吧，Bail和Barg？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Bail",
        "Barg"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，Bail和Barg是主备关系，互相做故障转移。另外它们都要接收来自Risk节点的流量信号。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Bail",
        "Barg",
        "Risk",
        "Signal"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，Bail和Barg双向连接，Risk通过Signal节点指向Barg。那Signal和Risk之间是什么关系？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Risk",
        "Signal",
        "Barg"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Risk是风险检测模块，它产生Signal信号。还有Place节点，它是压力测试入口，直接触发Press操作。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Risk",
        "Signal",
        "Place",
        "Press"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "Place到Press，这是一条独立链路。那WorkerNode呢？Code节点应该放在哪里？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Code",
        "Place",
        "Press"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Code是WorkerNode，它要依赖Etcd做服务发现，所以Code指向Define。同时Define也要通知Barg做路由更新。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Code",
        "Define",
        "Barg"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加Code到Define，以及Define到Barg。我检查一下——Audit、Bail、Code、Define这几个主节点都齐了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Audit",
        "Bail",
        "Code",
        "Define"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，Barg到Bail的箭头方向我刚才说反了。应该是Barg指向Bail，表示备用向主注册，不是双向对等。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Barg",
        "Bail"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "修正了，现在Barg单向指向Bail。那Bail还要指向Barg吗？还是只有这一条？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Bail",
        "Barg"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "保留双向，但方向要区分：Barg→Bail是注册，Bail→Barg是心跳检测。这样故障转移逻辑才完整。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Bail",
        "Barg"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，最终确认：Audit、Bail、Barg、Code、Define为主节点，Place-Press、Risk-Signal-Barg、Define-Barg为关键链路，Bail-Barg双向主备。结构清晰了。",
